{"tid":968685,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"日本女生最愛的中港台男神！「他」打敗楊洋奪下第一帥","createTime":"2019-01-04T12:18:53.000Z","updateTime":"2019-01-04T13:52:20.000Z","uid":9573,"like":4,"dislike":8,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"41edc59f21f4f0355f574afdcea786775d540cc9","tid":968685,"uid":9573,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-04T12:18:53.000Z","msg":"繼美國電影網站《TC Calendar》公布全球百大美男美女引發話題，日本網路論壇《Girls Channel》近日也熱烈回應「想看亞洲帥哥」的討論串，並以按讚投票的方式，為喜愛的亞洲男藝人給予支持，同時也引起大陸網友好奇「誰紅到日本？」<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn2.ettoday.net/images/3808/d3808437.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn2.ettoday.net%2Fimages%2F3808%2Fd3808437.jpg&h=be5a1790&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n▲日本女性網站討論起心中愛慕的中港台男神，楊洋、王鶴棣被點名。<br />\n<br />\n日本網友發起討論「想看各種亞洲帥哥（いろんなアジアのイケメンが見たい）」，其中新版《流星花園》的「道明寺」王鶴棣奪下631票，20歲、183CM的嫩齡和高挑身材吸讚數最狂；23歲的「花澤類」官鴻也有250票，陸版F4的顏值被盛讚：「全都超過180cm的人站在一起真是壓倒性的強。」<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn2.ettoday.net/images/3808/d3808419.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn2.ettoday.net%2Fimages%2F3808%2Fd3808419.jpg&h=85262d24&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n▲王鶴棣奪下631票，在討論串中是第一高票。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn2.ettoday.net/images/3808/d3808421.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn2.ettoday.net%2Fimages%2F3808%2Fd3808421.jpg&h=6f4e0a54&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n▲官鴻因《流星花園》狂吸250票。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn2.ettoday.net/images/3808/d3808422.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn2.ettoday.net%2Fimages%2F3808%2Fd3808422.jpg&h=e1c10db7&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n▲日本女性對陸版《流星花園》選角都180cm相當讚嘆。<br />\n<br />\n此外，楊洋因《微微一笑很傾城》在日本打開知名度，被形容「中國演員中少見的鹽臉帥哥。」超人氣偶像鹿晗則被強調「年收超過30億日幣。」轉型的陳曉被視為野性帥哥，黃子韜、張藝興、TF BOYS也在討論串中。香港有劉德華被狂讚「完全看不出來已經還曆（快60歲）！」<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn2.ettoday.net/images/3808/d3808428.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn2.ettoday.net%2Fimages%2F3808%2Fd3808428.jpg&h=7001117f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n▲楊洋因《微微一笑很傾城》爆紅，被日本網友形容「罕見的鹽臉帥哥。」<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn2.ettoday.net/images/3808/d3808434.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn2.ettoday.net%2Fimages%2F3808%2Fd3808434.jpg&h=30d51073&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n▲鹿晗「年收超過30億日幣。」<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn2.ettoday.net/images/3808/d3808430.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn2.ettoday.net%2Fimages%2F3808%2Fd3808430.jpg&h=b49f1e89&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n▲張藝興。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://www.hkcnews.com/news_%E6%96%B0%E8%81%9E/hk-discuss/2018/07/%E6%A2%81%E5%9C%8B%E9%9B%84-%E8%BF%BD%E8%A8%8E%E8%96%AA%E6%B4%A5-20180731175249_24f0.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.hkcnews.com%2Fnews_%25E6%2596%25B0%25E8%2581%259E%2Fhk-discuss%2F2018%2F07%2F%25E6%25A2%2581%25E5%259C%258B%25E9%259B%2584-%25E8%25BF%25BD%25E8%25A8%258E%25E8%2596%25AA%25E6%25B4%25A5-20180731175249_24f0.jpg&h=7cf7717e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n▲粱國雄。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn2.ettoday.net/images/3808/d3808436.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn2.ettoday.net%2Fimages%2F3808%2Fd3808436.jpg&h=72f0170e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n▲陳曉被歸為野性帥哥。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn2.ettoday.net/images/3808/d3808425.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn2.ettoday.net%2Fimages%2F3808%2Fd3808425.jpg&h=eb0404ae&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n▲劉德華被讚「看不出來快60歲！」<br />\n<br />\n台灣版《流星花園》對日本觀眾深有共鳴，當年扮演「道明寺」的言承旭至今仍有169票，「花澤類」周渝民的憂鬱眼神也有338票。曾到日本發展的炎亞綸、陳柏霖，「飛輪海」時期的吳尊、王子邱勝翊、到大陸拍古裝劇走紅的霍建華也都被點名，網友還抗議說：「台灣帥哥這麼多，日本的電視都看不到啊！」<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn2.ettoday.net/images/3808/d3808420.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn2.ettoday.net%2Fimages%2F3808%2Fd3808420.jpg&h=a3e40aca&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n▲言承旭憑《流星花園》仍風靡櫻花妹。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn2.ettoday.net/images/3808/d3808424.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn2.ettoday.net%2Fimages%2F3808%2Fd3808424.jpg&h=27ae0430&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n▲周渝民憂鬱眼神獲得338票。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn2.ettoday.net/images/3808/d3808426.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn2.ettoday.net%2Fimages%2F3808%2Fd3808426.jpg&h=658b034d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n▲炎亞綸曾赴日發展。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn2.ettoday.net/images/3808/d3808427.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn2.ettoday.net%2Fimages%2F3808%2Fd3808427.jpg&h=a92103d3&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n▲吳尊因「飛輪海」走紅全亞洲。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn2.ettoday.net/images/3808/d3808431.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn2.ettoday.net%2Fimages%2F3808%2Fd3808431.jpg&h=78351e17&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n▲陳柏霖拍過日劇。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn2.ettoday.net/images/3808/d3808435.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn2.ettoday.net%2Fimages%2F3808%2Fd3808435.jpg&h=fc7f10ed&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n▲王子也入榜。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn2.ettoday.net/images/3808/d3808429.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn2.ettoday.net%2Fimages%2F3808%2Fd3808429.jpg&h=bcab11e1&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n▲日網稱讚台灣帥哥多，日本電視都看不到。"},{"pid":"16aee6e652b29b5cef45f903c9787741f4111a96","tid":968685,"uid":99700,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-04T12:22:55.000Z","msg":"言承旭明明-182"},{"pid":"0afe07143e541c04664e74d395e04b4f82630559","tid":968685,"uid":91833,"like":20,"dislike":0,"score":20,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-04T12:28:29.000Z","msg":"粱國雄<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ab9aa4782e71cb20824b300664c0cbcf9c8286dd","tid":968685,"uid":89931,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-04T12:30:11.000Z","msg":"做乜言承旭咁多負皮"},{"pid":"35633f69660e152acbedab4d115c095aea3746b8","tid":968685,"uid":228963,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-04T12:31:23.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"2c3f5ae85f537cac94fc00f657ea0ab9902416da","tid":968685,"uid":5055,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-04T12:32:44.000Z","msg":"長毛<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"28d41cdfc1ddf9e1f0a99dd95450b09946de88d4","tid":968685,"uid":1239,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-04T12:35:58.000Z","msg":"你話死唔死。。。香港仲係講緊劉華 就60<br />\n人哋大陸台灣都係二三十代<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cf0f504bfa1a53b1fc042000ddd39d6bc3fcb2e7","tid":968685,"uid":80814,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-04T13:34:27.000Z","msg":"《流星花園》最窮道明寺有多窮？送遊戲金幣當禮物，飛機也不坐&hellip;&hellip;<br />\n<br />\n新版《流星花園》剛出來就造成大家熱烈的討論，除了劇情中有非常多的改變，最令觀眾介意的就是「道明寺變窮了」不過編劇後來有出來響應，主要是<span style=\"color: red;\">因為國家廣電總局的禁令「不准炫富、不准提錢、不准有貧富差距...等等」</span><br />\n<br />\n整部戲拍到一半限制才來的，既然如此~那我們就以幽默的心態來看看道明寺哪裏變窮了吧(笑)<br />\n<br />\n《流星花園》中最經典的一段，道明寺要求杉菜當他的女朋友，並用非常價值觀的言論來吸引她，記得2001年的道明寺連巴黎鐵塔都可以買給大S，想不到2018年的金錢上節省了很多...<br />\n<br />\n▼像是每年只能出去旅遊一次，或是上課的時候只能買零食飲料給她吃<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://i1.kknews.cc/SIG=2miib97/ctp-vzntr/1532084513410pp104s00q6.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi1.kknews.cc%2FSIG%3D2miib97%2Fctp-vzntr%2F1532084513410pp104s00q6.jpg&h=cbdbb303&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n▼最重要的是道明寺還說~打遊戲還會送用不完的遊戲金幣給杉菜<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://i1.kknews.cc/SIG=1b9b6ki/ctp-vzntr/1532084513643s07rnn3r50.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi1.kknews.cc%2FSIG%3D1b9b6ki%2Fctp-vzntr%2F1532084513643s07rnn3r50.jpg&h=03a6104a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n除了最窮道明寺之外~網友也分析表示本次的劇情也創造了「史上最有錢杉菜」<br />\n<br />\n▼網友紛紛表示：「上海房價這麼高，但杉菜家的坪數和裝修完全不像原作設定的窮苦人家，父母還能在街道開一家快餐店，而且杉菜考上明德學院後，爸爸還能請鄰里鄉親喝喜酒呢」(哈)<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://i1.kknews.cc/SIG=1oetlqv/ctp-vzntr/1532084514590846n1on02s.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi1.kknews.cc%2FSIG%3D1oetlqv%2Fctp-vzntr%2F1532084514590846n1on02s.jpg&h=d691c42b&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"0c57a293ad75b29da6b19a210f7a979a4b31f648","tid":968685,"uid":70274,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-04T13:45:06.000Z","msg":"不准炫富、不准提錢都算<br />\n連有貧富差距都唔提得  只報喜不報憂<br />\n只提國家永遠富強無貧窮<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"508e97d46a1f9efd2b56672cce0cb6839fb51c3b","tid":968685,"uid":80814,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-04T13:48:37.000Z","msg":"Btw，入到嚟想睇千雪，竟然變長毛<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4b3a007e200450e519eaee0740dddb225ddee75a","tid":968685,"uid":87394,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-04T13:50:59.000Z","msg":"冇陳偉霆?"},{"pid":"502e41a488d6c648f8e94fb5d3e8d10bcdf55671","tid":968685,"uid":1482,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-04T13:52:20.000Z","msg":"呢個真 日本d電視一打開9成老餅 同香港差不多"}]}